ActYouth Criminal Justice Act
SubjectGovernment of the Provinces and Territories ** Financial Agreements **
PrecisOrder (1) Repealing paragraph (b) of Order in Council P.C. 2013-0353 of March 28, 2013; and (2) Approving that the Minister of Justice to ENTER into new five-year CONTRIBUTION AGREEMENTS from April 1, 2018 to March 31, 2023 with provinces and territories in order to continue contribution funding through the Youth Justice Services Funding Program and the Intensive Rehabilitative Custody and Supervision Program.
